quran[8{c,v,t}:
12,96,"phir jab khoo sh khaberi laane wala aaya to is ne yousuf ka kameez yaqoob ke munh par daal diya aur yaka yak is ki benaye Aud kar aayi tab is ne kaha"" mein tum se kehta nah tha? mein Allah ki taraf se woh kuch jaanta hon jo tum nahi jantay """
12,97,"sab bol utthay"" abba jaan, aap hamaray gunaaho ki bakhshish ke liye dua karen, waqai hum khata car thay """
12,98,"uss ne kaha"" mein apne rab se tumahray liye maffi ki darkhwast karoon ga, woh bara maaf karne wala aur Raheem hai """
12,99,"phir jab yeh log yousuf ke paas puhanche to uss ne apne walidain ko apne sath bitha liya aur ( apne sab knbe walon se ) kaha"" chalo, ab shehar mein chalo, Allah ne chaha to aman chain se raho ge """
12,100,"( shehar mein daakhil honay ke baad ) is ne apne walidain ko utha kar apne paas takhat par bithaya aur sab is ke agay be ikhtiyar sjday mein jhuk gay yousuf ne kaha"" abba jaan, yeh tabeer hai mere uss khawab ki jo mein ne pehlay dekha tha, mere rab ne usay haqeeqat bana diya is ka ahsaan hai ke uss ne mujhe qaid khanaay se nikala, aur aap logon ko sehraa se laa kar mujh se milaya halaank shetan mere aur mere bhaiyon ke darmain fasaad daal chuka tha waqea yeh hai ke mera rab ghair mehsoos tadbeeron se apni Mushiyat poori karta hai, be shak o hay Aleem aur hakeem hai"
12,101,"ae mere rab, to ne mujhe hukoomat bakhsh aur mujh ko baton ki teh taq pohanchna sikhaya zameen o aasman ke bananay walay, to hi duniya aur akhirat mein mera sarparast hai, mera khtama islam par kar aur injaam car mujhe salheenke sath mila """
12,102,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, yeh qissa ghaib ki khabron mein se hai jo hum tum par wahi kar rahay hain warna tum uss waqt mojood nah thay jab yousuf ke bhaiyon ne aapas mein ittafaq kar ke saazish ki thi"
12,103,magar tum khuwa kitna hi chaho inn mein se aksar log maan kar dainay walay nahi hain
